document_title: What is gonorrhea? Causes and warning signs
subsection_name: benh-lau.json_9_3. Treatment of gonorrhea in newborns
subsection_content: A mother with gonorrhea can transmit it to her baby during birth. In this case, doctors often prescribe treatment with antibiotics.
